university.name: University Oxford
university.description: Oxford is a collegiate University, there are 38 Colleges and 6 Permanent Private Halls. Each is independent and self-governing. Each runs and maintains its own website, each website will look different.

university.name: University Harvard
university.description: Harvard’s Graduate School of Arts and Sciences has both struggled with inclusion and made monumental strides for equity and opportunity throughout its history.

university.name: University Stanford
university.description: Stanford is renowned for the quality of its teaching, its wealth and its proximity to Silicon Valley, home to some of the most important high-tech companies. It is considered one of the top ten universities in the world.
